superheroes.title: Superheroes
superheroes.description: All your favorite comic book captains and caped crusaders

300444.title: Agent Cody Banks
300444.description: Cody Banks seems like an average teenage boy, except for one thing: He's a CIA secret agent. Can he balance math homework, girls, and covert ops?

310501.title: Superheroes
310501.description: What if superheroes were real? Meet the real-life, self-proclaimed crime fighters who don masks and capes and attempt to bring justice to evildoers.

383416.title: X-Ray & Vav: Seasons 1 & 2
383416.description: Two friends play superhero, protecting the city from a greedy half-pirate, half-corporate villain and a mad scientist bent on world domination.

389503.title: Robocop
389503.description: A cop who died in the line of duty is transformed into a chrome-plated cyborg policeman with an indestructible new body and a thirst for revenge.

389506.title: Robocop 2
389506.description: In a dystopian Detroit, drug dealers run rampant. Cyborg cop Alex Murphy returns to take on both a crime boss and a twisted version of his own self.

406602.title: Afro Samurai: Resurrection
406602.description: After finding peace, Afro Samurai is forced back into the game by sexy Sio, a deadly woman from his past who won’t quit until he pays for his sins.

457139.title: Super Detention
457139.description: Troublemakers at a superhero school escape from detention to save their fellow students from an evil villain who wants to steal their powers.

460992.title: Antboy 2
460992.description: Antboy returns to his crime-fighting ways and his world thrust into danger when a new band of super-villains arise to attack him and attempt revenge.

461702.title: Antboy 3
461702.description: Problems start piling up for Antboy when a skateboarding superhero steals his thunder, and his former foe The Flea returns with a vengeance.

462344.title: Firefly
462344.description: Firefly features a mix of Singaporean and Malaysian comedians, a gratuitous comedic plot and a righteous story structure. The film tells the story of a righteous afa who turns himself into a superhero, but he has no super power. And hired a superhero assistant and another set of villain superheroes to fight criminals for society. This is a fashion movie based on the concept of fighting criminals and featuring superheroes. So there will be American superhero costumes, multiple actors playing superheroes in a play, and there will be cool superhero costumes. In American superhero movies, the heroes all prefer tight clothing, which shows the beauty of their muscular lines, exudes male grandeur and reveals part of their face.

465051.title: Rendel: Dark Vengeance (English Sub)
465051.description: A masked vigilante named Rendel wages war against VALA, a sinister global corporation that won't stop at murder to silence its foes.

465294.title: Guardians (English Sub)
465294.description: Formed during the Cold War, an elite squad of superheroes return to action when new threats arise that threaten the safety of the world.

465295.title: Guardians (English Dub)
465295.description: Formed during the Cold War, an elite squad of superheroes return to action when new threats arise that threaten the safety of the world.

466377.title: Masters of the Universe
466377.description: A brave warrior must free a beautiful sorceress imprisoned by an evil ruler, but the key has been hidden on Earth and found by a teenage duo.

486887.title: Warriors of Virtue
486887.description: After a young boy enters a strange world, he meets five noble, wise and loyal Kung Foo kangaroos who teach him his own strengths as they fight evil.

519919.title: Invisible Sue
519919.description: In a scientific accident, a teenager gains the power of invisibility and uses her newfound superhero strengths to save her mother from kidnappers.

523582.title: Valentine: The Dark Avenger
523582.description: A cafe waitress who dreams of acting is recruited by men she believes to be filmmakers, but who transform her into a real masked anti-crime heroine.

525178.title: Rise of the Superheroes
525178.description: The exciting, unauthorized story of comic book superheroes and their leap from the page to the screen, from Batman to Iron Man and Black Panther.

531302.title: Elf-Man
531302.description: Super-hero “Elf-Man” helps some kids save their dad’s invention from a bumbling gang of thieves and have the best Christmas ever.

546360.title: Kamen Rider Heisei Generations Forever
546360.description: Kamen Rider Zi-O and Kamen Rider Build join forces with all of the other Heisei Generation Riders to reverse the damages of an evil Time Jacker.

555004.title: Loser Hero
555004.description: Superhero powers and a shocking twist follow in this story of a downtrodden loser who becomes a hero when he’s bestowed with incredible abilities.

555283.title: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Maximum Overload
555283.description: Spider-Man, Wolverine and other Marvel superheroes take on a mischievous Loki and a team of super villains in an all-new LEGO adventure.

555284.title: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes: Avengers Reassembled!
555284.description: The Avengers are forced to “party” with Ultron when he seeks to disassemble the team and take over the world by hijacking Iron Man's armor.

556082.title: Ultraman Orb the Movie: Let Me Borrow the Power of Bonds!
556082.description: A villainous space witch allies with Ultraman Orb’s archenemy to use The Dark Ring and capture the Ultra Warriors as jewels in her collection.

556234.title: Ultraman Geed the Movie: Connect the Wishes!
556234.description: Ultraman Geed’s hasty actions put the Ultraman team in danger when they face off against an army intent on wiping out intelligent lifeforms.

560769.title: Ultra Fight Orb
560769.description: A hateful Ghost Sorcerer meets his match in a in a mega-powerful Orb who can use lighting and fusion attacks to fight the spirits of dead monsters.

561901.title: Zebraman (Subbed)
561901.description: A depressed man's alter ego becomes his saving grace after he uses his fantasy persona to battle criminals and an intergalactic conspiracy.

562727.title: Bravestorm
562727.description: A remake of two series pits two families, a robotic bionic superhero, and a giant red robot against alien evil forces, to stop mankind's extinction.

565417.title: Zebraman (Dubbed)
565417.description: A lazy teacher turns to cosplay in the streets to be like his favorite childhood TV superhero, only to find that the villains from the show are real.

572441.title: Ultraman X the Movie
572441.description: Our team of superheroes faces off against a diabolical monster and its army of giant kaijus after a reality TV host steals a coveted precious gem.

588324.title: Professor Marston and the Wonder Women (En)
588324.description: Here’s the true origins story of a modern-day feminist superhero – Wonder Woman – and the psychologist-inventor who created the powerful character.

589323.title: Superhero Movie
589323.description: In this hilarious parody of beloved blockbusters, a nerdy teenager is bitten by a radioactive dragonfly, which gives him superhuman abilities.

593736.title: Captain Monsterica And The Purple Protector
593736.description: Our fearless superheroes not only take on bad guys, but they also go on the most fun and radical missions ever, all while working together.

601184.title: The Lawnmower Man (Director's Cut)
601184.description: Dr. Lawrence Angelo (Pierce Brosnan) is a brilliant scientist obsessed with perfecting virtual reality software. When his experiments on animals fail, he finds the ideal substitute – Jobe Smith (Jeff Fahey), a slow-witted gardener.

601188.title: Ultraman Ginga S the Movie: Showdown! The 10 Ultra Warriors!
601188.description: The Super Dimensional Demon Etelgar forces a beautiful young alien princess to use her magic to trap Ultraman all across the galaxy! In order to stop Etelgar and save their fellow Ultra Heroes, two brave young men named Hikaru and Sho must transform into Ultraman Ginga and Ultraman Victory. But will even their combined powers be enough to defeat Etelgar and his army?

601189.title: Ultra Fight Victory
601189.description: After thousands of years, a diabolical space emperor named Juda Spectre is about to break free from his dimensional prison! In order to prevent this disaster from happening, and to save the Galaxy, Earth's amazing superhero ULTRAMAN VICTORY must use a new secret weapon, a combination sword and flute called the Knight Timbre! However, can the soundwave strength of our Ultraman's Knight Timbre stop Spectre and his army of monsters before it's too late?!

605474.title: Ultraman R/B the Movie: Select! the Crystal of Bond
605474.description: After finally achieving peace, Isami and Asahi move towards their dreams, but discover that the path forward is full of distractions and challenges.

606516.title: RoboCop 3
606516.description: A heartless corporation kicks families out of their Motor City homes, inspiring RoboCop to bring his skills to a team of freedom fighters.

606552.title: Ultraman Zero: The Revenge of Belial
606552.description: An evil army threatens the entire known galaxy, which forces Ultraman Zero and his team to band together and fight before it's too late.

608156.title: The Lawnmower Man (Theatrical Cut)
608156.description: In his quest to create the ultimate virtual reality software, a computer scientist finds his perfect human guinea pig in a slow-witted gardener.

623205.title: Antboy
623205.description: When bitten by a super-ant, a 12-year old boy transforms into an extraordinary superhero, who must face a super-villain to rescue a kidnapped girl.

632980.title: Kamen Rider Zero-One: Real Time
632980.description: This long-awaited spin-off of “Kamen Rider Zero-One” finds a mysterious new rider with a cult of followers cheering his terrorism across the world.

636895.title: Batman
636895.description: After the Pearl Harbor attack, a pair of costumed secret agents are tasked with foiling a Japanese spy’s plan to mind-control American scientists.

655405.title: The Toxic Avenger
655405.description: The free-for-all crime spree comes to an end for evil-doers after a meek mop boy falls into a vat of toxic waste and turns into a mutated superhero.

665895.title: Corrective Measures
665895.description: As tensions rise among supervillain inmates and corrupt staff, the march toward anarchy begins in the world’s most dangerous maximum-security prison.

667954.title: Ultraman Saga
667954.description: A decade and a half after Shin Asuka, the Earth has been taken over by the mysterious Alien Batt with only a few humans left fighting to survive.

668165.title: Alpha Rift
668165.description: When a magic helmet thrusts Nolan into a world of modern-day knights fighting supernatural evil, he's forced to become the hero he was destined to be.

671653.title: Mega Monster Battle: Ultra Galaxy: The Movie
671653.description: Three million light years from Earth on Planet M-78, Ultraman joins forces with allies to fight an army of giant monsters led by Ultraman Belial.

675101.title: Lawnmower Man 2: Beyond Cyberspace
675101.description: They thought they had destroyed him. What they didn’t count on was the simple gardener-turned-superkiller finding a way to reboot himself.

680111.title: The Awakener
680111.description: After a personal tragedy, a Brazilian federal agent becomes a masked vigilante crusading against corrupt politicians and businesses.

686242.title: Green Ghost
686242.description: Destiny forces a secret group of Mexican superheroes to bring their adopted gringo car salesman and TV personality into their fight to save humanity.

690819.title: My Babysitter the Superhero
690819.description: Two siblings find that the gregarious old lady taking care of them while their mom is away is actually the legendary superhero Agent Action.

693384.title: The Toxic Avenger Part II
693384.description: The monster superhero is tricked into going to Tokyo to search for his estranged father, leaving Tromaville open to domination by an evil corporation.

693394.title: The Toxic Avenger Part III: The Last Temptation of Toxie
693394.description: When Toxie finds he has nothing to do as a superhero, he goes to work for a major corporation that he learns may be the evilest of all his foes.

693968.title: Heroes of the Galaxy
693968.description: A group of sixth graders find a laptop with an unusual adventure game, Heroes of the Galaxy, and discover a secret portal to enter the game world.

696437.title: Steamboy
696437.description: In 1860s Britain, a boy inventor finds himself caught in the middle of a deadly conflict over a revolutionary advance in steam power.

708393.title: The Return of Captain Invincible
708393.description: When arch criminal Mr. Midnight plots to take over the world, humanity's only hope is a retired WWII superhero who is now a burned-out drunk.

100002882.title: The Amazing Spider-Man
100002882.description: Teenage outcast Peter Parker grapples with bullying at his high school and amazing super-human crises as his alter-ego, Spider-Man.

01009.title: Batman Unlimited
01009.description: A series of shorts from the Batman Unlimited series of Batman's greatest battles and team-ups against his gallery of rogue villains.

0300008596.title: Birds of Prey
0300008596.description: After Batman leaves New Gotham City, It’s up to Barbara Gordon aka Batgirl, Helena The Huntress, and a metahuman named Dinah to save the day.

0300007606.title: Ultraman Taro
0300007606.description: Kotaro Higashi is a young man who had just returned to Japan after finishing a long voyage.

04710.title: NightMan
04710.description: After being struck by lightning, a jazz musician gains the power to telepathically sense evil and becomes his city's nocturnal superhero.

01096.title: New Adventures of Nanoboy
01096.description: Think its tough being the little guy?  Then try saving the world when youre tinier than the average cell!The new adventures of Nanoboy is an action-comedy about a boy who transforms into the worlds smallest superhero to fight microscopic villains too small for the naked eye!  In the micro-cosmos, the tiny world of cells, molecules and atoms, a battle of good versus evil rages as Nanoboy takes on the Amazonian Amoebas, deranged proteins and bad-to-the-bone-bacteria  while trying to survive the biggest ch

0300005115.title: Kamen Rider: Kuuga
0300005115.description: Godai Yusuke must use a telepathic connection to transform into the warrior Kuuga and defend mankind from ferociously powerful monsters.

0300007490.title: Cardcaptor Sakura
0300007490.description: A fun-loving 10-year-old who lives with her brother and widowed father becomes a collector of magical cards when she makes a glowing discovery.

03504.title: Mirai Sentai Timeranger
03504.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! It's the 30th century and time travel is illegal. To help monitor and police time crimes, the Time Protection Department is founded. But when Don Dolnero and his nefarious gang manage to trick four new TPD cadets into allowing them travel to the 20th century, the four cadets are forced to pursue them for the sake of history. There, in a time foreign to them, the cadets enlist Tatsuya Asami, a young martial artist, to aid their mission. Together, these five youngsters become the Timerangers. And though they try to live as ordinary 20th-century citizens, the Timerangers dedicate their lives to stopping Dolnero and others that may follow in his footsteps, attempting to forever alter the proper timeline!

01072.title: Ultraman
01072.description: Hayata, one of the Science Patrol's members, holds the key to our salvation. Fate has given Hayata the ability to secretly transform into an amazing, super-powered giant from space. A being known as Ultraman!

01855.title: PreCure
01855.description: Nagisa Misumi is an outstanding athlete and daring girl that doesn't take time to study but has a very strong sense of justice. Honoka Yukishiro is an honor-roll student always boasting the best grades in her class. The two are 8th graders at the Verone Junior High School for girls. Nagisa and Honoka each encounter Mepple and Mipple – two mysterious creatures who came down from the sky one night. These two strange creatures grant Nagisa and Honoka the power to transform into superheroes called "Cure Black" and Cure White", and thus the two girls become guardians of planet Earth.

01983.title: Tiger & Bunny
01983.description: The city of Stern Bild is protected by corporate superheroes known as NEXT, who fight crime while promoting their sponsors on the popular show “HERO TV.” Veteran hero Wild Tiger relies on his years of experience and instincts to fight crime, but his tendency to destroy public property for the sake of protecting the lives of the innocent has earned him the nickname “Crusher for Justice.” Now, under orders from his new employer, Wild Tiger finds himself forced to team up with Barnaby Brooks Jr., a rookie with an attitude. Two polar opposites work to fight evil in this thrilling buddy-hero action series!

0300009151.title: Ultraman Tiga
0300009151.description: A high-tech defense team protects Earth from monsters and alien invaders with the help of the giant super-being Ultraman Tiga.

0300007925.title: Kamen Rider Ryuki
0300007925.description: Action-packed adventure series from Japan where superhero fighters known as Kamen Riders fight monsters in a mirrored portal world.

03135.title: Kyuukyuu Sentai GoGoFive
03135.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! After the Bowzock, a ruthless-not to mention reckless- gang of interstellar biker thugs, destroy his home planet of Hazard, Dappu visits Earth where he discovers five humans with the ability to harness "Carmagic." With this power, these five heroes can defeat the Bowzock before the band of witless bikers is able to add Earth to its list of wrecked worlds.

0300006474.title: Ultraman Ace
0300006474.description: The Ultraman saga continues in this 1972 series that sees the new Ultraman Ace fight off the alien Yapool and his Terrible Monsters on planet Earth.

0300008154.title: Voltron Force
0300008154.description: Five robotic lions piloted by the Voltron Force come together to form a super robot that fights against evil, taking down one bad guy at a time.

01831.title: Captain Harlock
01831.description: The year is 2977. Mankind has become complacent and stagnant. All work is done by machines, while humans spend all their time on entertainment.

0300004950.title: Legacy of the Silver Shadow
0300004950.description: A group of students are thrown together as modern-day crime-fighters after discovering the underground headquarters of a long-forgotten superhero.

0300009152.title: Ultraman Zero: The Chronicle
0300009152.description: Son of the legendary Ultra Seven, rookie Ultraman Zero receives training from his master Ultraman Leo on his way to becoming a qualified fighter.

0300005414.title: Ultraforce
0300005414.description: Superheroes are commissioned by the U.S. government to protect the world from their terrorist counterparts, who have evil plans to take over.

02180.title: Chouriki Sentai Ohranger
02180.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! It is the year 1999. The Machine Empire of Baranoia, led by Emperor Bacchus Wrath, has invaded Earth with the intention of wiping out all human life and bringing about machine rule. Chief Counsellor Miura of the UAOH (United Airforce Overtech Hardware), in a desperate attempt to quell this invasion, has revived super energies born of the lost civilization of Pangaea. Enlisting an elite squad of the finest officers the UAOH has to offer, Miura has harnessed Tetrahedron Power, granting the team the power to transform into the Ohrangers, and save humanity from its darkest crisis yet!

0300009149.title: Ultraman Dyna
0300009149.description: The Year: 2017. Humanity has built settlements throughout the solar system to begin the conquest of unknown lands.

01117.title: Super Sentai Zyuranger
01117.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! Ky_ry_ Sentai Zyuranger is a Japanese tokusatsu television series and the sixteenth installment in the long-running Super Sentai franchise of superhero programs.

0300006320.title: Ultraman X
0300006320.description: Fifteen years after a deadly accident claimed the lives of his parents, a scientist decides to pursue justice by transforming into a powerful hero.

0300008061.title: Gridman the Hyper Agent
0300008061.description: After 3 tech-savvy kids create their own videogame superhero they find that their creation is being controlled by a digital cop named Gridman.

0300008057.title: Ultraman 80
0300008057.description: A junior high science teacher who moonlights as a member of the elite Utility Government Members keeps Earth safe from alien and monster attacks.

0300009153.title: Ultraseven X
0300009153.description: An amnesiac receives a pair of spectacles that enable him to transform into a red giant and fight off alien forces threatening human society.

02409.title: Ultraman Leo
02409.description: Alien intergalactic slavers called Magma come to Earth in an attempt to find more slaves for their expanding evil empire. In response, the Ultra Warriors send Leo to protect the planet from this new threat.

0300008062.title: The Ultraman
0300008062.description: This 1979 anime series was the first Ultraman franchise that wasn’t live-action as our hero helps the Science Guard Agency investigate UFOs.

0300008702.title: Buck Rogers
0300008702.description: A 20th Century pilot and his young friend buddy awake from 500 years of suspended animation.

0300009756.title: Grounded
0300009756.description: Following the outbreak of a global virus, the world’s most powerful superhero finds himself quarantined at home, where he couldn’t be more useless.

0944.title: Gerry Anderson: Thunderbirds
0944.description: Operating from a top-secret island base in the year 2065, the team at International Rescue- intrepid Jeff Tracy and his valiant sons Scott, John, Virgil, Gordon, and Alan- engage in a never-ending humanitarian crusade to protect the innocent.

0300009110.title: Ultra Zero Side Story: Killer the Beatstar
0300009110.description: Ultimate Force Zero, made up of Ultraman Zero and others visit Princess Emerana. However, Princess Emerana is taken by a giant artificial planet.

04749.title: The Aquabats! Super Show!
04749.description: A rock band consisting of five superheroes battle monsters in a retro campy style, complete with fake commercials and the heroes in cartoon form.

0300008056.title: Kamen Rider Zero-One
0300008056.description: The action series about a young man on his bike heading to an amusement park who doesn’t know he’ll become a cyborg crimefighter for the ages.

04068.title: The Greatest American Hero
04068.description: After losing the instructions to his superhero suit, a school teacher becomes a clumsy crime fighter with the help of his girlfriend and an FBI agent.

03042.title: Seijuu Sentai Gingaman
03042.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! Three millennia after the first invasion of the Space Pirates Barban, a new set of Gingamen - Hyuuga, Gouki, Hayate, Hikaru, Saya - have been selected to protect the Earth. That is, unless the Barban are able to disrupt the ceremony!

0300005659.title: The Daichis: Earth's Defense Family (Dubbed)
0300005659.description: An average Japanese nuclear family with above-average internal conflict is chosen to serve as the planet’s protectors against an invading alien force.

0300007116.title: Ultraman Ginga
0300007116.description: A high schooler returns home after seven years of adventures overseas and has his life changed by a talking Ultraman Taro doll he discovers.

03663.title: The Adventures of Napkin Man
03663.description: A new kind of superhero leaps off the page and to life to help children better understand their feelings.

04750.title: Ultraman Geed
04750.description: The story of a teenager who inherits the evil Ultraman's genes, but never loses sight of friendship and a strong will to become a true hero.

0300008373.title: Animorphs
0300008373.description: When Earth has been invaded by a race of mind-controlling aliens, it’s up to five teenagers and their ability to morph into animals to save humanity.

0300007168.title: Sidekick
0300007168.description: Most kids dream of being superheroes. Not Eric Needles. Eric dreams of being a sidekick. So you can imagine his elation when his favorite superhero, Maxum Man, selects Eric to be his sidekick. But things take a weird turn when, on the day that Eric is scheduled to start being a full-time sidekick, Maxum Man vanishes.

03859.title: Black Scorpion
03859.description: A city police detective takes to the streets as the vigilante Black Scorpion after her father is shot by a corrupt district attorney.

0300007288.title: Flash Gordon
0300007288.description: The classic 1950s sci-fi series featuring Flash Gordon and his Galaxy Bureau investigators taking on monsters, alien rulers, and more in the universe.

02927.title: Gekisou Sentai Carranger
02927.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! After the Bowzock, a ruthless-not to mention reckless- gang of interstellar biker thugs, destroy his home planet of Hazard, Dappu visits Earth where he discovers five humans with the ability to harness "Carmagic." With this power, these five heroes can defeat the Bowzock before the band of witless bikers is able to add Earth to its list of wrecked worlds.

03400.title: Afro Samurai
03400.description: He's a legend with an ice cold soul and a jones for revenge: Afro Samurai. As a kid, he saw his father slaughtered. Now a man, Afro journeys to the mountain to face destiny. The perpetrators are gonna get what they deserve. Starring Samuel L. Jackson.

03665.title: Captain Flamingo
03665.description: Armed with a backpack of novelty gags, Milo saves the day as proudly pink superhero Captain Flamingo, with a little help from his best pal Lizbeth.

04787.title: The Daichis: Earth's Defense Family (Subbed)
04787.description: A dysfunctional family of four become the reluctant superhero saviors of the planet when an extraterrestrial invasion threatens all life on Earth.

0300005855.title: The Greatest American Heroine
0300005855.description: In this pilot movie for a revival of “The Greatest American Hero," superhero Ralph Hinkley choses a female successor, much to Bill Maxwell’s dismay.

04106.title: Ninpuu Sentai Hurricaneger
04106.description: After tragedy strikes on graduation day at the Ninja Academy, three pupils waste no time taking on the clan of evil space warriors responsible.

04751.title: Ultraman Orb
04751.description: A hero battles extraterrestrial threats with the power of the Orb Ring which turns him into a warrior of light, Ultraman Orb.

0300006872.title: Sheena
0300006872.description: ‘Baywatch’ star Gena Lee Nolin stars in this series as Sheena, Queen of the Jungle, whose magical powers are used to protect her animal kingdom.

0300007232.title: Ultraman R/B
0300007232.description: Two brothers who don’t always see eye to eye are transformed by ultra powers as their peaceful city is attacked by a fire-breathing monster.

0300006348.title: Ultraman Orb the Origin Saga
0300006348.description: In this origins series from the Ultraman universe comes the tale of two young men whose friendship and quest for greatness turns into a bitter feud.

0300009150.title: Ultraman Gaia
0300009150.description: A wormhole in space forms just outside the Earth's atmosphere and monstrous creatures descend upon the world's cities.

03696.title: Hyakujuu Sentai Gaoranger
03696.description: Five color-coded warriors are called upon to protect Earth from the monstrous Orgs, who have reignited their war on humanity after a long silence.

0300007110.title: Ultraman Ginga S
0300007110.description: 2 years after the final battle in Furuhoshi which took place in the presequel "Ultraman Ginga", the time arrives for Hikaru Raido to have another fateful encounter with the mysterious warrior, Ultraman Victory, and a new invading force from space. With the help of the special task force UPG, Hikaru unites with Ultraman Ginga again to forge a path to the future, and a titanic tale of battles begins to unfold!

0300006353.title: Return of Ultraman
0300006353.description: The 1971 TV series featuring the original superhero Ultraman and Ultraseven as they protect earth from a new attack by aliens and monsters.

02308.title: Denji Sentai Megaranger
02308.description: Shout! Factory TV presents Super Sentai! When his video game prowess is discovered by I.N.E.T., high school student Kenta Date is brought in to lend his expertise to their mysterious research. Meanwhile, four classmates show up, wanting to know more about the I.N.E.T. facility. Their experience will change their lives forever, as I.N.E.T. survives an attack by the nefarious Dr. Hinelar and an army from another dimension determined to conquer our reality!

0300009081.title: Ultra Galaxy Legend Side Story: Ultraman Zero vs Darklops Zero
0300009081.description: After landing on a random planet, Captain Hyuga of Zap Spacy and Rei are confronted unexpectedly with the fake Ultraman and Ultra Seven.
